replies.body:
It sounds like you're experiencing an unstable connection to the servers. When the client's connection to the servers drops off or becomes poor, it will cause delays in what you see in champ select or even crash you to the desktop. The most common solutions for this issue can be found on our [connection guide.
](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues)

Let me know if this guide helped solve the issue.
